<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Login Page</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">

    <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Login as</p>

    <div class="bg-primary flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center h-30vh mb-6" style="height: 30vh;">
        <!-- <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.xZy01t2g2X1yYA_GaCG7zQHaEL?w=270&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.4&pid=1.7]]" alt="Description of Image" class="w-1/2 h-auto md:mr-4" /> -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="text-aliceblue">Success</h1>
            <p class="text-white">
                Success is no accident. It is hard work, perseverance, learning, studying, sacrifice, and most of all, love of what you are doing or learning to do.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-around mb-12 px-4">
        <div class="bg-black text-white p-6 rounded shadow-lg w-full md:w-1/3 mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Teacher Login Section</h2>
            <p>This is for staff login. From here you can manage student details, remove, and add records.</p>
            <button type="button" class="bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded shadow hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-300 mt-4">
                <a href="/teacher/login" class="flex items-center justify-center">Teacher Login</a>
            </button>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: darkblue;" class="bg-darkblue text-white p-6 rounded shadow-lg w-full md:w-1/3">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Student Login Section</h2>
            <p>
                Here you can access your academic journey with ease through our personalized gateway to success, where you can see <strong>results</strong>: instantly view your results module-wise and <strong>track progress</strong>.
            </p>
            <button type="button" class="bg-green-500 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded shadow hover:bg-green-600 transition duration-300 mt-4">
                <a href="/student/login" class="flex items-center justify-center">Student Login</a>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
